{"tid":2008320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係咪唔記得五大訴求有啲咩","createTime":"2020-05-09T03:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T03:15:21.000Z","uid":282188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"10d983d1da9c29a90099ce662cee2cf6dad7110c","tid":2008320,"uid":282188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家就係connect藍絲要成立獨立調查委員會嘅時候</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7eT1Rd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7eT1Rd.jpg&h=514bf07b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我支持警察執法！呢啲只係害群之馬，唔代表全部警察！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你又知呢啲只係害群之馬而唔係冰山一角？你諗下政府撥左15億OT錢，呢班人都有得袋，不如將啲錢每人派多3000蚊好？<br />\n<br />\n藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁啲警察好辛苦ot咁拉暴徒，冇佢地香港就亂嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：但佢地有啲係自編自導自演扮暴徒掟汽油彈，姐係你出糧俾佢搞亂香港喎，咁都得咩？<br />\n<br />\n藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：呢啲只係個別事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：[直入式廣告] 要知道呢啲係咪個別事件，其實成立<span style=\"color: pink;\">獨立調查委員會</span>就得嫁啦！有左獨立調查委員會，就知道邊啲人有扮示威者呃ot，邊啲人知法犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣要人！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我要獨立調查委員會！</span></span>"},{"pid":"43564dec99eef13040915a0ecc96a5216c7258c5","tid":2008320,"uid":282188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:13:54.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215ab76d96020d81f97959fd5b966af0176a5ca2","t